data.description: Welcome home! This stunning single-family home is in the pleasantly serene Via Verde 55+ Community with a low HOA. Step into the welcoming open floor-plan living room which is light and bright with vaulted ceilings. It is accentuated by the presence of a darling dining area with abundant windows that serve as the perfect spot for intimate dinners or special gatherings.  As for the kitchen, these stunning views overlook the well maintained complex with all its beauty of greenery and its tranquil atmosphere. It is equipped with a pantry and ample cabinets for all your cooking supplies. Accompanied by oversized large bedrooms with spacious closets. Venture outdoors, and you'll be greeted by two delightful patios areas. Designed to serve as a perfect canvas for your gardening imagination and an ideal area for your morning coffee or  to enjoy a delightful evening dinner.  Storage and parking needs are catered to without a hassle, via the convenient, attached two-car garage. This space provides not only a secured spot for your vehicles, but also extra storage for your belongings within easy reach. Join the Via Verde community and experience quiet and friendly living while enjoying all the diverse amenities this beautiful neighborhood has to offer. Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity!
